---
import { site } from '../content/site';
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="border-t border-border bg-background px-4 py-12">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-6 md:flex-row md:justify-between">
      <!-- Brand -->
      <div class="text-center md:text-left">
        <a href="/" class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-foreground">OMYQT</a>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground">{site.tagline}</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Links -->
      <nav class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
        <a href="/blog" class="transition-colors hover:text-foreground">블로그</a>
        <a href={site.appUrl} class="transition-colors hover:text-foreground">앱 시작하기</a>
        <a href={`mailto:${site.contact.email}`} class="transition-colors hover:text-foreground">문의하기</a>
      </nav>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col items-center gap-4 border-t border-border pt-8 md:flex-row md:justify-between">
      <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">
        &copy; {year} OMYQT. All rights reserved.
      </p>
      <div class="flex gap-4 text-xs text-muted-foreground">
        <a href={site.contact.privacyUrl} class="transition-colors hover:text-foreground">개인정보처리방침</a>
        <a href={site.contact.termsUrl} class="transition-colors hover:text-foreground">이용약관</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-6 text-center text-xs text-muted-foreground/60">
      OMYQT는 AI가 보조하는 묵상 도우미입니다. 신앙적 결정은 본인의 판단과 교회 공동체 안에서 이루어져야 합니다.
    </p>
  </div>
</footer>
